<p>CameraServer code would look something like just the putVideo portions of <a href="https://docs.wpilib.org/en/stable/docs/software/vision-processing/roborio/using-the-cameraserver-on-the-roborio.html#advanced-camera-server-program">this example</a>.</p>
<pre data-code-wrap="java"><code class="lang-java">// create the output stream
CvSource outputStream = CameraServer.putVideo("MyImage", 640, 480);
// create a mat
Mat mat = new Mat(640, 480, 3);
// load your image into mat as a RGB image, using OpenCV

while (!Thread.interrupted()) {
  outputStream.putFrame(mat);
  Thread.sleep(500);
}

